  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This character can no longer be flanked. This defense denies a rogue the ability to sneak attack the character by flanking her, unless the attacker has at least four more rogue levels than the target has class levels.</p>\n<p>If a character already has <em>uncanny dodge</em> (see above) from another class, the levels from the classes that grant <em>uncanny dodge</em> stack to determine the minimum rogue level required to flank the character.</p>"
